==假說==
根據該星的[[恆星光譜|恆星光譜]]可知，該星的亮度變化不可能是它本身的變化，即此星並非[[變星|變星]]。<ref name="arXiv:1509.03622" />因此，科學家提出了數個假說，假設有某些物體在環繞該星並阻擋它的光，但是尚沒有一個假說可以完整解釋觀察到的資料。

某些假說認為這和資料{{link-en|偽缺陷|Artifact (error)}}有關，有些認為是[[宇宙塵|宇宙塵]]，有極大環形結構的氣體行星<ref name="AT-20151016" /><ref name="FRB-20151016">{{cite news |url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/ethansiegel/2015/10/16/bizarre-star-kic-8462852-an-alien-paradise-or-a-catastrophic-wasteland/ |title=No, Astronomers Probably Haven't Found 'Alien Megastructures' |work=[[Forbes|Forbes]] |last=Siegel |first=Ethan |date=2015-10-16 |accessdate=2015-10-17 |archive-date=2017-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170812104447/https://www.forbes.com/sites/ethansiegel/2015/10/16/bizarre-star-kic-8462852-an-alien-paradise-or-a-catastrophic-wasteland/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>近期捕捉到的[[小行星帶|小行星帶]]、<ref name="arXiv:1509.03622" />、進行中的[[後期重轟炸期|後期重轟炸期]]等。<ref name="NASA-20151124"/><ref name="Lisse2015">{{cite journal |title=IRTF/SPeX Observations of the Unusual Kepler Light Curve System KIC8462852 |journal=The Astrophysical Journal Letters |first1=Carey |last1=Lisse |first2=Michael |last2=Sitko |first3=Massimo |last3=Marengo |volume=815 |issue=2 |at=L27 |date=December 2015 |doi=10.1088/2041-8205/815/2/L27 |bibcode=2015ApJ...815L..27L |arxiv=1512.00121}}</ref>

===被成形中的物質環繞的恆星===
[[File:Artist’s_Impression_of_a_Baby_Star_Still_Surrounded_by_a_Protoplanetary_Disc.jpg|thumb]]
Boyajian諮詢了天文學家傑森·萊特（Jason Wright），<ref name="UT-20151016" /><ref name="Laker">{{cite news |url=http://home.bt.com/news/science-news/alien-megastructure-may-explain-light-patterns-from-bizarre-star-say-scientists-11364010755958 |script-title=en:‘Alien megastructure’ may explain light patterns from ‘bizarre’ star, say scientists |work=BT.com |first=Chris |last=Laker |date=16 October 2015 |accessdate=17 October 2015 |archive-date=2017-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170729215247/http://home.bt.com/news/science-news/alien-megastructure-may-explain-light-patterns-from-bizarre-star-say-scientists-11364010755958 |dead-url=no }}</ref>他和其他研究KIC 8462852的人在一篇後續的研究報告中提出，如果該星比其位置和速度透露的年紀還年輕，那麼它可能還有物質在周遭成形。<ref name="PSU-20151015" />

{{link-en|NASA紅外線望遠鏡設施|NASA Infrared Telescope Facility}}（NASA IRTF）在0.8–4.2[[微米|微米]]光譜下對該恆星系的觀察，在數個[[天文單位|天文單位]]的距離內沒有發現任何成形中物質的跡象。<ref name="NASA-20151124"/><ref name="Lisse2015"/>

===行星殘骸場===
[[File:PIA18469-AsteroidCollision-NearStarNGC2547-ID8-2013.jpg|thumb]]
目前已經對該星進行了高解析度的[[光譜學|光譜儀]]和影像觀察，也透過西班牙的{{link-en|北歐光學望遠鏡|Nordic Optical Telescope}}進行了[[光譜能量分布|光譜能量分布]]分析。<ref name="arXiv:1509.03622"/><ref name="AT-20151016">{{cite web |last=Rzetelny |first=Xaq |script-title=en:Something—we’re not sure what—is radically dimming a star’s light No satisfying explanations, but guesses range from comets to colliding planets. |url=http://arstechnica.com/science/2015/10/something-were-not-sure-what-is-radically-dimming-a-stars-light |date=16 October 2015 |work=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]] |accessdate=17 October 2015 |archive-date=2015-10-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151018155448/http://arstechnica.com/science/2015/10/something-were-not-sure-what-is-radically-dimming-a-stars-light/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>如果這些環繞恆星的物體之間發生碰撞，那麼應該會產生溫暖的塵埃，並發出[[紅外線|紅外線]]光，但是目前並沒有觀察到任何超量的紅外線能量，因此這些物體不可能是巨大行星之間碰撞產生的殘骸。<ref name="SLT-20151015"/>其他研究者認為行星殘骸場的解釋是行不通的，因為克卜勒望遠鏡觀察到這個現象的機會非常低。<ref name="arXiv:1509.03622" />

===分解的彗星群產生的雲氣===
[[File:PIA20053-PossibleCometSwarmAroundKIC8462852-ArtistConcept-20151124.jpg|thumb]]
其中一個解釋該星奇異的亮度變化的假說是，有一群崩解的[[彗星|彗星]]雲氣以橢圓形軌道環繞該星。<ref name="arXiv:1509.03622" /><ref name="PS-20151013">{{cite news |url=http://www.popsci.com/have-we-detected-alien-megastructures-around-distant-star |title=Have We Detected Megastructures Built By Aliens Around A Distant Star? Or Just A Cloud Of Comets? Scientists Want To Investigate Further |work=[[Popular_Science|Popular Science]] |last=Fecht |first=Sarah |date=13 October 2015 |accessdate=14 October 2015 |archive-date=2017-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170601033925/http://www.popsci.com/have-we-detected-alien-megastructures-around-distant-star |dead-url=no }}</ref>在這個假設情境下，來自周遭恆星的重力可能造成該星的[[歐特雲|歐特雲]]裡的彗星朝該星墜落。支持這個假說的證據是，距離該星{{convert|885|AU|e9km|0|order=flip|sp=us|lk=out}}確實有一顆[[紅矮星|紅矮星]]存在。但是，來自歐特雲的彗星雲氣被重力擾動後，以橢圓形軌道近距離繞行恆星，並且有足夠的數量造成該星22%的亮度下降，這個想法是受到質疑的。<ref name="SLT-20151015" />

===人工巨型結構===
[[File:Dyson_Swarm_-_2.png|thumb]]
